        'My chronic illness flares without warning. Some days I can do everything. Some days I cannot get out of bed.',
        '',
        'Teachers and coaches saw me at my best and assumed I was capable at that level all the time. When I crashed, they thought I was being lazy.',
        '',
        'My 504 plan has flexible attendance and assignment extensions. But invoking it on a bad day required energy I did not have.',
        '',
